{
  "texts": [
    "Each weekly web-based section for PA and diet will last about 15 minutes.",
    "In the first week, once the participants complete the faceto-face intervention, the researcher will immediately organize a web-based intervention course for older adults at the PA gymnasium and the senior center for diet, respectively.",
    "The researcher will first introduce the website's content and then demonstrate the steps to use this web-based program.",
    "Afterward, research helpers will guide participants in accessing the website and finishing the online study.",
    "In the 2nd week, the web-based intervention course will be continuously offered at the gym and the senior center to ensure older adults are familiar with the website's usage."
  ]
}